      "title": "Julian Bolling summoned to CID",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Criminal Investigations Department (CID) today summoned Sri Lankan medal-winning swimmer Julian Bolling to record statements for the future investigation following the incident where the private residence of President Ranil Wickremesinghe was set ablaze on July 9."
